import React from 'react'; import Anchor from '../../Generic'; import Img from '../../../assets/images/OurStory.png'; import Kategory from '../../Kategory/index' import { Container, Title, Text, Wrapper, Image } from './style'; export const OurStory = () => { return ( <> Our Story CargoPrime corparation is a transportation company that was established in Pittsburgh, PA in 2018. Our company acknowledges the strong potential of the trucking industry to make a big impact on business and society. Our management team with 15 years of transportation experience and professional drivers work to meet your needs and provide excellent customer service.

CargoPrime corparation provides a flexible solution, on-time service, safe and experienced drivers, tracking on expedited services. We promise to provide world-class transportation services and ensure your freight is delivered on schedule and straight to the designated destination. Our goal is your satisfaction with our services. We welcome you to check out our website and discover our services: Freight transportation, CDL Drivers, Employee job opportunities. ); }; export default OurStory;
